{"title":"","uid":"f73a8e23e6f6f669cf99c7dba8fa0722","slug":"Web Dev/Front End/02. svg","date":"2023-03-07T16:14:46.386Z","updated":"2020-11-29T09:53:34.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Web Dev/Front End/02. svg.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<ol>\n<li>svg————可缩放矢量模型（scalable vector graphics）</li>\n<li>svg的主要意义：svg生成矢量图，它不会随着图片的缩放而发生失真<br>##使用svg</li>\n<li>使用 <embed> 标签导入 <pre class=\"line-numbers language-html\" data-language=\"html\"><code class=\"language-html\">&lt;embed src&#x3D;&quot;circle1.svg&quot; type&#x3D;&quot;image&#x2F;svg+xml&quot; &#x2F;&gt;</code></pre></li>\n<li>直接在html中嵌入svg代码 <pre class=\"line-numbers language-html\" data-language=\"html\"><code class=\"language-html\">&lt;svg xmlns&#x3D;&quot;http:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.w3.org&#x2F;2000&#x2F;svg&quot; version&#x3D;&quot;1.1&quot;&gt;\n   &lt;circle cx&#x3D;&quot;100&quot; cy&#x3D;&quot;50&quot; r&#x3D;&quot;40&quot; stroke&#x3D;&quot;black&quot; stroke-width&#x3D;&quot;2&quot; fill&#x3D;&quot;red&quot; &#x2F;&gt;\n&lt;&#x2F;svg&gt;</code></pre></li>\n<li>链接svg文件 <pre class=\"line-numbers language-html\" data-language=\"html\"><code class=\"language-html\">&lt;a href&#x3D;&quot;circle1.svg&quot;&gt;View SVG file&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;</code></pre>\n##svg的图形元素</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>引出：svg有很多预定义的形状元素，可以直接被开发者使用和操作！</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li><p>矩形————<rect></p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15